// Ownership Endpoints

### Get All Ownerships
GET http://localhost:3000/api/ownerships

### Get Ownership by ID
GET http://localhost:3000/api/ownerships/1

### Get Ownership by ID (not found)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/ownerships/99999

### Get Ownership by ID (invalid ID)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/ownerships/invalid

### Get Ownership History by Stove
GET http://localhost:3000/api/stoves/1/ownership-history

### Get Ownership History by Stove (invalid ID)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/stoves/invalid/ownership-history

### Get Player's Ownerships
GET http://localhost:3000/api/players/1/ownerships

### Get Player's Ownerships (invalid ID)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/players/invalid/ownerships

### Create Ownership (lootbox)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/ownerships
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "stoveId": 1,
    "playerId": 1,
    "acquiredHow": "lootbox"
}

### Create Ownership (trade)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/ownerships
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "stoveId": 1,
    "playerId": 2,
    "acquiredHow": "trade"
}

### Create Ownership (mini-game)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/ownerships
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "stoveId": 1,
    "playerId": 1,
    "acquiredHow": "mini-game"
}

### Create Ownership (invalid acquiredHow)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/ownerships
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "stoveId": 1,
    "playerId": 1,
    "acquiredHow": "stolen"
}

### Create Ownership (missing fields)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/ownerships
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "playerId": 1,
    "acquiredHow": "lootbox"
}

### Get Current Owner
GET http://localhost:3000/api/stoves/1/current-owner

### Get Current Owner (not found)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/stoves/99999/current-owner

### Get Current Owner (invalid ID)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/stoves/invalid/current-owner

### Delete Ownership
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/ownerships/1

### Delete Ownership (not found)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/ownerships/99999

### Count Ownership Changes
GET http://localhost:3000/api/stoves/1/ownership-changes/count

### Count Ownership Changes (invalid ID)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/stoves/invalid/ownership-changes/count

### Count Stoves Acquired by Player
GET http://localhost:3000/api/players/1/acquired-stoves/count

### Count Stoves Acquired by Player (invalid ID)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/players/invalid/acquired-stoves/count
